# Cloudflare Pages response headers, applied to every path: baseline security
# headers against clickjacking, MIME sniffing, and referrer leakage. (No CSP —
# the inline theme-init script in layout.tsx would need a per-request nonce/hash,
# and a misconfigured CSP failing closed is a worse risk than its marginal
# benefit on a static marketing page.)
/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
